<pre>I've also been in touch with them via email - totally agree that it's
a combination of 2.0 and apps.

I intend to work on just about everything except the FB plugin for
them if we can work out the details.  The &quot;let reporters edit their
own reports&quot; plugin is something that I've been thinking about for
months now.

Before I get into it, is anyone currently working on any of the
following features:

- Alerts by category
- Detailed report info in map infobox
- Search reports by category (or any other parameter for that matter)
- Allow reporters to edit reports they create

george

