<span class="ez_quot">&gt; My question is if there is a code available for the following things we</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; would like to implement:</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; - the possibility to send alerts from the map only for some categories (I</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; saw that e.g. Haiti ushahidi has implemented</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; it <a href="http://haiti.ushahidi.com/alerts);</span>">http://haiti.ushahidi.com/alerts);</span></a>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; - the possibility for the user to be able to see a list of names of reports</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; when s/he clicks on a cluster of reports on the map (this was implemented</span>
